1. *Oluja* se nadvija nad gradom. (A storm is looming over the city.)
2. *Oluji* će biti potpuno okončano za dva dana. (The storm will be completely over in two days.)
3. *Olujom* je sve ostalo uništeno. (Everything was destroyed by the storm.)
4. Pokušao je da se zaštiti od *oluje*. (He tried to protect himself from the storm.)
5. Očekuje se da će *oluja* uskoro stići. (It is expected that the storm will soon arrive.)